title: The Office XXX Parody
description:
Office manager Michelle introduces a camera crew to her underlings at Dunder Muffin, where everybody seems to have relationships with one another. And when Michelle hires a stripper to give a lecture on sexual harassment behind Toby from the HR department's back, the already sexually laden atmosphere in the work place explodes.
